Two communities existing worlds apart and affected by the breast cancer disease are examined. One community is surrounded by affluence and technology, while the other is affected by poverty, stigma, and inadequate healthcare. These two communities share one thing in common, a threat to mankind- breast cancer.

Courage To Dare hopes to impact the african community by changing the perception about breast cancer disease, encourage regular medical exams and self exams.  The more this target market understands about breast cancer and how they have the power through early detection, we hope that death rates will decrease.
